This directory contains demos and tests running on the BEPM engine controller.

Available demos and tests:
+-demo_Mini-BDM-Pod.dbug12.txt   This is the BEPM port of the S12CBase demo.
|                                It reads SCI input and prints the read value in
|                                ASCII, hexadecimal, decimal, octal, and binary 
|                                representation. The SCI runs at 9600 baud with
|                                XON/XOFF flow control.
|                                This ASCII file contains all D-Bug12 commads to
|                                run the demo in the on-chip RAM. No flashing
|                                required.
|
+-demo_Mini-BDM-Pod.dbug12.lst   The assembler listing of the LRE demo code.
|
+-demo_Mini-BDM-Pod.flash.s28    This is a flashable S-record of the demo code.
|
+-demo_Mini-BDM-Pod.flash.lst    The assembler listing of the flashable demo
                                 code.

